room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Excido Escape Room in Los Angeles
room_address: 6593 Collins Drive, Ste D 13  Moorpark, CA 93021
room_description: You are meeting your friend at his cabin for a weekend retreat up in the mountains. But when you arrive, you hear a cryptic message. Your friend has been arrested and the cops are on the way to the cabin. See if you can find your friend's treasured keepsakes and get out, before the cops arrive and you join your friend behind bars.
